      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single scratch or smudge in sight\u2014the interior is totally spotless and it runs like a total dream. If you're looking for something that's been kept in truly perfect shape, this is the one for you! I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'm happy to chat!",
