    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 993 Carrera, the pinnacle of air-cooled engineering. This example features the M64/21 3.6L flat-six with the VarioRam induction system, providing optimized volumetric efficiency across the power band. The G50 6-speed manual transaxle offers precise throws, transmitting power to the rear wheels via a factory-optioned limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its LSA (Lightweight-Stable-Agile) multi-link rear suspension, maintaining original kinematic geometry. Mechanically flawless, the engine exhibits zero seepage at the timing chain covers or valve gaskets, and the underside is remarkably dry. The original paint maintains deep luster with no evidence of thermal cycling on the plastic trim. A documented history of preventative maintenance ensures this 911 performs with the same tactile feedback as it did on the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
