    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections, further protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no creasing, and the factory-fresh scent persists. Every electronic feature and driver aid functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history exclusively through authorized dealerships. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full fluid service and a fresh set of high-performance tires. Included with the sale are both original keys, the factory window sticker, and all service receipts. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that satisfies the most meticulous inspection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
